 2008-07922008-04-18,  EC,  ,  , 
ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
PrecisRegulations Amending the GASOLINE REGULATIONS by extending until January 1, 2010 the exemption with respect to leaded gasoline imported, produced or sold for use in competition vehicles. This extension will permit the industry to move forward with planned 2008 events, while providing time for the government to further study the health risks of leaded gasoline use at Canadian race tracks.
